headline: How Recent Moves Are Rewriting The Story For Baxter International (BAX)
summary: Baxter International’s latest price target work keeps the fair value estimate clustered around US$23.13 per share, with only a small adjustment to the discount rate and revenue growth assumptions. This signals that recent information has not materially reshaped the core story in the models behind that number. Street research is still split between the low US$20s and US$30 range, but there is clear focus on how upcoming Q4 results and the 2026 outlook might either confirm or challenge the...
